        "summary": "In the millennial day, all men will praise the Lord\u2014He will dwell among them\u2014Compare 2\u00a0Nephi 22.",
        "chapterAugmentations": [],
        "verses": [
            {
                "text": "And in that day thou shalt say, O Lord, I will praise thee: though thou wast angry with me, thine anger is turned away, and thou comfortedst me.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "2\u00a0Ne. 22:1 (1\u20136).",
