                        "start": 4,
                        "end": 15
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "IE\u00a0The people who are gathered will sing this song of praise.",
                        "start": 32,
                        "end": 33
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "Behold, God is my salvation; I will trust, and not be afraid: for the Lord Jehovah is my strength and my song; he also is become my salvation.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Priesthood, Power of; Strength.",
                        "start": 89,
                        "end": 97
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Salvation.",
                        "start": 132,
                        "end": 141
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 12,
                        "end": 14
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 83,
                        "end": 85
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 102,
                        "end": 104
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "Therefore with joy shall ye draw water out of the wells of salvation.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Joy.",
                        "start": 15,
                        "end": 18
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "And in that day shall ye say, Praise the Lord, call upon his name, declare his doings among the people, make mention that his name is exalted.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Thanksgiving.",
                        "start": 30,
                        "end": 36
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "OR\u00a0proclaim.",
                        "start": 47,
                        "end": 56
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "Sing unto the Lord; for he hath done excellent things: this is known in all the earth.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
